{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1564,"text":"What you're doing,"},{"time":3335,"text":"right now, at this very moment,"},{"time":6139,"text":"is killing you."},{"time":8159,"text":"More than cars or the Internet"},{"time":10914,"text":"or even that little mobile device we keep talking about,"},{"time":13683,"text":"the technology you're using the most almost every day"},{"time":16574,"text":"is this, your tush."},{"time":19780,"text":"Nowadays people are sitting 9.3 hours a day,"},{"time":22909,"text":"which is more than we're sleeping, at 7.7 hours."},{"time":26407,"text":"Sitting is so incredibly prevalent,"},{"time":28272,"text":"we don't even question how much we're doing it,"},{"time":30249,"text":"and because everyone else is doing it,"},{"time":33191,"text":"it doesn't even occur to us that it's not okay."},{"time":35965,"text":"In that way, sitting has become"},{"time":38277,"text":"the smoking of our generation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42181,"text":"Of course there's health consequences to this,"},{"time":44609,"text":"scary ones, besides the waist."},{"time":47390,"text":"Things like breast cancer and colon cancer"},{"time":51042,"text":"are directly tied to our lack of physical [activity],"},{"time":54331,"text":"Ten percent in fact, on both of those."},{"time":56963,"text":"Six percent for heart disease,"},{"time":58483,"text":"seven percent for type 2 diabetes,"},{"time":60506,"text":"which is what my father died of."},{"time":63286,"text":"Now, any of those stats should convince each of us"},{"time":65347,"text":"to get off our duff more,"},{"time":66966,"text":"but if you're anything like me, it won't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69736,"text":"What did get me moving was a social interaction."},{"time":72964,"text":"Someone invited me to a meeting,"},{"time":74272,"text":"but couldn't manage to fit me in"},{"time":75445,"text":"to a regular sort of conference room meeting, and said,"},{"time":78283,"text":"\"I have to walk my dogs tomorrow. Could you come then?\""},{"time":82108,"text":"It seemed kind of odd to do,"},{"time":84155,"text":"and actually, that first meeting, I remember thinking,"},{"time":86265,"text":"\"I have to be the one to ask the next question,\""},{"time":88029,"text":"because I knew I was going to huff and puff"},{"time":91185,"text":"during this conversation."},{"time":93369,"text":"And yet, I've taken that idea and made it my own."},{"time":96499,"text":"So instead of going to coffee meetings"},{"time":98145,"text":"or fluorescent-lit conference room meetings,"},{"time":100373,"text":"I ask people to go on a walking meeting,"},{"time":103403,"text":"to the tune of 20 to 30 miles a week."},{"time":107342,"text":"It's changed my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109771,"text":"But before that, what actually happened was,"},{"time":113000,"text":"I used to think about it as,"},{"time":113982,"text":"you could take care of your health,"},{"time":115678,"text":"or you could take care of obligations,"},{"time":118202,"text":"and one always came at the cost of the other."},{"time":122007,"text":"So now, several hundred of these walking meetings later,"},{"time":125139,"text":"I've learned a few things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126512,"text":"First, there's this amazing thing"},{"time":128386,"text":"about actually getting out of the box"},{"time":131111,"text":"that leads to out-of-the-box thinking."},{"time":133085,"text":"Whether it's nature or the exercise itself, it certainly works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137510,"text":"And second, and probably the more reflective one,"},{"time":140530,"text":"is just about how much each of us"},{"time":142825,"text":"can hold problems in opposition"},{"time":145289,"text":"when they're really not that way."},{"time":147264,"text":"And if we're going to solve problems"},{"time":148972,"text":"and look at the world really differently,"},{"time":150570,"text":"whether it's in governance or business"},{"time":152699,"text":"or environmental issues, job creation,"},{"time":155561,"text":"maybe we can think about how to reframe those problems"},{"time":158224,"text":"as having both things be true."},{"time":160426,"text":"Because it was when that happened"},{"time":162349,"text":"with this walk-and-talk idea"},{"time":163804,"text":"that things became doable and sustainable and viable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167763,"text":"So I started this talk talking about the tush,"},{"time":169743,"text":"so I'll end with the bottom line, which is,"},{"time":173753,"text":"walk and talk."},{"time":175384,"text":"Walk the talk."},{"time":176667,"text":"You'll be surprised at how fresh air drives fresh thinking,"},{"time":180335,"text":"and in the way that you do,"},{"time":181931,"text":"you'll bring into your life an entirely new set of ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185459,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187186,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}